        <headline>Special Weather Statement issued August 14 at 3:44PM EDT by NWS Blacksburg VA</headline>
        <description>At 344 PM EDT, radar indicated strong thunderstorms were located
along a line extending from Glasgow to Arcadia to near Fincastle.
Movement was southeast at 10 mph.

Wind gusts up to 50 mph are possible with these storms.

Locations impacted include...
Buchanan...
Glasgow...
Clifford...
Big Island...
Montvale...
Fincastle...
and Coleman Falls.
</description>
